      "text": {
        "content": [
          "<div class='er_lead md:er_lead-md'><h3>About the Summit</h3><p>When a crisis hits, we look for systems of support & collaboration that go beyond the status quo.</p><p>At this online summit we gather together people who deploy policies, infrastructures, tools, business activity and community projects that can form an essential support system for sustaining livelihoods in times of crisis.</p></div>",
          "<div class='er_list md:er_list-md'><h4>This event is designed to help participants‚Ä¶</h4><ul><li>üí¨ Find the right conversations</li> <li>üìù Grow their professional network</li> <li>üõ† Build new income opportunities</li> <li>üìñ Learn from others‚Äô past experiences</li> <li>üß≠ Explore new models for securing resilient livelihoods</li></ul></div>"
        ],
